  "abstract": "The International Crops Research Institute for the Semi-Arid\r\nTropics (ICRISAT) is pleased to publish this bulletin as a\r\nservice to scientists, students and agriculturists concerned\r\nwith the improvement of cereals and farming systems throughout\r\nAsia, Africa and Latin America. The genetic improvement of\r\npearl millet is one of ICRISAT's major projects and — along\r\nseveral other millets - figures prominently in our research\r\nprogram on farming systems.",
